graph TD
    subgraph SplitBrainRisk ["SPLIT-BRAIN RISK (No Fencing)"]
        NN1[NameNode 1 - Believes it is ACTIVE] -->|Writes stale edits| QJM[JournalNodes Quorum]
        NN2[NameNode 2 - Promoted to ACTIVE] -->|Writes conflicting edits| QJM
        QJM -->|Result: Metadata Corruption!| Conflict[Conflicting transactions accepted]
    end

    subgraph PreventSplitBrain ["PREVENTING SPLIT-BRAIN (With Fencing & Epochs)"]
        S_NN1[NameNode 1 - Epoch: 10]
        S_NN2[NameNode 2 - Promoted to ACTIVE - Epoch: 11]
        
        S_NN2 -->|1. Increment Epoch on JournalNodes| S_QJM[JournalNodes Quorum]
        Note over S_QJM: JournalNodes lock epoch to 11. <br/>Reject all writes with epoch < 11.

        S_NN1 -.->|2. Attempts stale write with Epoch 10| S_QJM
        S_QJM --x|3. REJECT WRITE (Epoch 10 < 11)| S_NN1
        
        S_NN2 -->|4. Active ZKFC triggers SSH Fence| Fence[Fence Action: Kill NameNode 1 process]
        Fence -->|Terminates| S_NN1
    end
